Troy WHEATHERSPOON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2025 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 14, 2017 SUAREZ, SALTER and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied. See Asay v. State, 769 So. 2d 974 (Fla. 2000).
